about.summary: A convenience function that delegates to the appropriate standard library function.

name: openfile
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "openfile" %}
{% set version = "0.0.7" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ea4e8f19112049f578ec161b12f70c1113144988c0a488ab173a138b50f37479

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.5
  run:
    - python >=3.5

test:
  imports:
    - openfile

about:
  home: https://github.com/luismsgomes/openfile
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A convenience function that delegates to the appropriate standard library function.
  doc_url: https://github.com/luismsgomes/openfile/blob/master/README.rst

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - monaldoj
